{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"60ace853ee","title":"给周恩来的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0b3781efb7","index":0,"year":1966,"month":12,"day":27,"articleId":"60ace853ee"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3457e40c94","name":"党内资产阶级","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ae92d43be4","type":"title","text":"给周恩来的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"60ace853ee"},{"id":"a60c01867c","type":"paragraph","text":"恩来同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"60ace853ee"},{"id":"cb8df970a5","type":"paragraph","text":"最近，不少来京革命师生和革命群众来信问我，给走资本主义道路的当权派和牛鬼蛇神戴高帽子、打花脸、游街是否算武斗？我认为：这种做法应该算是武斗的一种形式。这种做法不好。这种做法达不到教育人民的目的。这里我强调一下，在斗争中一定要坚持文斗，不用武斗，因为武斗只能触及人的身体，不能触及人的灵魂。只有坚持文斗，不用武斗，摆事实，讲道理，以理服人，才能斗出水平来，才能真正达到教育人民的目的。应该分析，武斗绝大多数是少数别有用心的资产阶级反动分子挑动起来的，他们有意破环党的政策，破坏无产阶级文化大革命，降低党的威信。凡是动手打人的，应该依法处之。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"60ace853ee"},{"id":"a16f90ece9","type":"paragraph","text":"请转告来京革命师生和革命群众。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"60ace853ee"},{"id":"ac74b0a35c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"60ace853ee"},{"id":"f69b5231c7","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六六年十二月二十七日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"60ace853ee"}],"page":{"id":"4324baefc5","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"60ace853ee","start":241,"end":241}}}},"__N_SSG":true}